# QA data dumps & binaries — bulky machine output, not source history, and
# may embed captured session tokens. ~330MB total (incl. 289MB live-RAG JSON +
# 10MB screenshots). The .md bug reports and .py/.js QA scripts ARE committed —
# just not the raw JSON captures or screenshots.
.collab/tasks/**/*.json
.collab/tasks/*.json
.collab/tasks/screenshots/
.collab/reviews/ui-audit-artifacts/

# Local agent tool state (not portable)
.agents/
